{
  "stem": "747.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I had not so much given that I should be hard to carry, you know, the weight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I enjoyed being-- it was a beautiful life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything that my father thought me was good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, the first year when it was came Yom Kippur and we had the go to say Yiskor, the memorial, you know, prayer for the death.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I ran out knowing very well that they are not coming back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was sort of-- I couldn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It took me slowly, slowly sunk in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how it is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And time goes on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know-- and when I started to talk, really, about it, that's what started the healing process.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Till then, I just tortured myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And why not the others?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like many others doing the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then I started to think that maybe-- Could you-- could you just--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--there was purpose of me being here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should be able to tell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because others, healthy ones, my friends--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you mean why did I survive?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why I am the one who, who was, was-- survived and the others didn't?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were healthy and they were young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have no answer for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only thing I feel now, that definitely since there's such a turmoil in the world, that definitely, I feel that it must have been a purpose of God to let me live, that I should be able to tell.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I see the response of the young people, especially what I am worried about the teenagers, with this, this neo-Nazis coming to defense and trying to sell them this garbage, this theory of super-- superhuman Nazi ideology, it makes me sick.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
